ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectNational Energy Board - The Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the National Energy Board to ENTER INTO A COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada for all employees in the bargaining unit to be effective from November 1, 2014 to October 31, 2018, pursuant to Section 112 of the FEDERAL PUBLIC SECTOR LABOUR RELATIONS ACT.
